1:19:34.682 --> 1:19:36.467
[body thuds]

1:19:38.861 --> 1:19:45.258
[panting] No! No!
No, let me go and take her.

1:19:45.302 --> 1:19:47.870
She's a lying little bitch
who killed our prophet!

1:19:47.913 --> 1:19:48.784
-You want me to kill her?

1:19:50.524 --> 1:19:52.439
