1:19:54.572 --> 1:19:56.095
-[Sunny screams]

1:20:00.447 --> 1:20:03.363
[panting]

1:20:08.455 --> 1:20:10.370
He'd kill me
without blinking.

1:20:10.414 --> 1:20:11.763
And you know it.

1:20:14.374 --> 1:20:17.943
-[grunting]

1:20:22.382 --> 1:20:23.644
-[breathing heavily]

1:20:23.688 --> 1:20:24.950
[shovel clanks]

1:20:29.215 --> 1:20:32.001
[breathing through mask]

1:20:37.920 --> 1:20:39.138
-You know you wouldn't
have survived

1:20:39.182 --> 1:20:41.010
