who ever lived!

1:20:44.752 --> 1:20:46.232
To take him from me, you--

1:20:46.276 --> 1:20:48.408
KARMA: [through mask]
Shut up!

1:20:48.452 --> 1:20:51.107
-You take everything
he gives you.

1:20:51.150 --> 1:20:53.326
