to decide who lives and dies.

1:20:57.461 --> 1:20:58.941
[Karma strains]

1:20:58.984 --> 1:21:00.290
-But you're worthless.

1:21:00.333 --> 1:21:02.988
You're a worthless
piece of shit.

1:21:03.032 --> 1:21:04.120
