1:21:06.252 --> 1:21:07.384
-[through mask] Shut up!

1:21:07.427 --> 1:21:08.559
-Yeah!

1:21:10.082 --> 1:21:11.649
[body thuds]

1:21:11.692 --> 1:21:18.003
[groaning] Why should I?

1:21:18.047 --> 1:21:20.614
Because Paul died
and made you queen?

1:21:20.658 --> 1:21:22.703
That's not how it works, honey--

1:21:22.747 --> 1:21:26.272
-[panting]

1:21:26.316 --> 1:21:29.145
